court.name: Supreme Court of the United States

attorneys: Motion of petitioner for reconsideration of order denying leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Georgia denied.
casebody.head_matter:
Waseem DAKER, petitioner,
v.
GEORGIA.
No. 15-9708.
Supreme Court of the United States
Dec. 12, 2016.
Motion of petitioner for reconsideration of order denying leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Georgia denied.
